name: Fluxbot
description: Fluxbot is Solana's #1 Telegram trading bot. Fluxbot facilitates next generation trading with lightning-fast swaps and snipers allowing users to buy and sell tokens across Solana, including for Token 2022/SPL+ tokens. Winner of Hyperdrive Hackathon (Grand Champion) at Solana Breakpoint 2023, and backed by Solana Foundation, Fluxbot features advanced algorithms and robust infrastructure with a built in AI assistant and rugcheck.
